

flowchart TD
    A[User enters username & password] --> B[Frontend sends credentials to Backend]
    B --> C[Backend queries Database for user]
    C --> D[Database returns user record with hashed password]
    D --> E[Backend compares entered password with hash]

    E -->|Valid| F[Generate auth token]
    F --> G[Return token to Frontend]
    G --> H[Frontend shows dashboard]

    E -->|Invalid| I[Return 401 Unauthorized]
    I --> J[Frontend shows error message]
